OL,3,CWednesday fan who mocked death of
OL,4,Csupporter in 'Hillsborough' tweet
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FA football supporter who appeared to
OL,8,Fmock the death of a rival fan in a
OL,9,Fsocial media post referencing the
OL,10,FHillsborough disaster has been
OL,11,Fsentenced.
OL,13,FRichard Crisp, 55, admitted sending an
OL,14,Findecent or offensive message over a
OL,15,Fpost on X after the death of West
OL,16,FBromwich Albion fan Mark Townsend.
OL,18,FMr Townsend, 57, fatally collapsed in
OL,19,Fthe Leppings Lane End when the two
OL,20,Fsides met at Hillsborough on 28
OL,21,FSeptember.
