OL,7,FAfter the match, Crisp appeared to
OL,8,Fmake a link to the 97 Liverpool fans
OL,9,Fwho died at the Hillsborough disaster
OL,10,Fin 1989.
OL,12,FHe wrote: "What are we at now, 98?
OL,13,FWhen we get to 100 we'll have a party."
OL,15,FAppearing at Sheffield Magistrates
OL,16,FCourt for sentencing, Crisp, of Lennox
OL,17,FRoad, Hillsborough, apologised for the
OL,18,F"upset and anger" he caused.
