OL,7,FThe married father of two was given a
OL,8,F12-month community order and ordered
OL,9,Fto pay #200 in costs as his family
OL,10,Fwatched from the public gallery.
OL,12,FCrisp's post caused outrage,
OL,13,Fespecially among West Brom fans, many
OL,14,Fof whom had witnessed distressing
OL,15,Fscenes in the stands after Mr Townsend
OL,16,Fwas taken ill during the Championship
OL,17,Fclash.
