OL,7,FMrs Brown also said her client and his
OL,8,Ffamily had been targeted with threats
OL,9,Fsince the incident, leaving them
OL,10,F"scared for their lives", and she
OL,11,Fadded: "It was quite clear someone was
OL,12,Fwatching their house."
OL,14,FMark Hughes, prosecuting, told
OL,15,Fmagistrates the police became involved
OL,16,Fafter the manager of Hillsborough Golf
OL,17,FClub, where Crisp was a member for 19
OL,18,Fyears, became concerned, especially
OL,19,Fafter someone with a Liverpool accent
OL,20,Fhad called threatening to "burn the
OL,21,Fclubhouse down".
