OL,7,FMr Hughes told the court that the
OL,8,Ffamily of Mr Townsend has not made a
OL,9,Fcomplaint.
OL,11,FHe is the third Sheffield Wednesday
OL,12,Ffan to be sentenced for communications-
OL,13,Fbased offences in a little over a year.
OL,15,FEarlier this month Brandon Pedryc was
OL,16,Ffined #300 and given a football
OL,17,Fbanning order after he held up a
OL,18,Fmessage at the Steel City derby
OL,19,Fmocking the recent death of former
OL,20,FSheffield United player George Baldock.
